            "title": "A股午後跌勢加劇  近全日低位收市 深股全周升逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午後跌幅擴大，以接近全日低位收市，兩市合計成交21468.86億元(人民幣‧下同)。一周計深累升逾1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指全日跌25點或0.65%，報3828點，今早開報3839，跌24點或0.62%，上午見3856點，升10點或0.26%，為全日高位，午後跌破上低位，並以全日低位收市，全日成交9278.65億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬股一周升8點或0.21%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指全日報13209，跌236點或1.75%，今早開報13394點，跌51點或0.38%，早段見13453，升8點或0.06%，為全日高位，隨即向下，午後低見13205，挫240點或1.75%，為全日低位，全日成交12190.21億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深股一周累升139點或1.06%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300全日跌43點或0.95%，報4550點，今早開報4576點，跌17點或0.37%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日跌64點或2.6%，報3151點，今早開報3222點，跌13點或0.4%。</p>\n</div>",
